\begin_layout Standard
The Krammers-Heisenberg-Driac (KHD) formula for Raman scattering cross section:
 (energy domain)
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{fi}\left(\omega_{I}\right)=\frac{8\pi\omega_{I}\omega_{S}^{3}}{9c^{4}}\sum_{\rho,\lambda}\left|\left[\alpha_{fi}\left(\omega_{I}\right)\right]_{\rho\lambda}\right|^{2}
\]

